    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230660/extras/8c05f830186b1c8af8d39993e08527a5.poster.avif?t=1746573644\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230660/extras/8c05f830186b1c8af8d39993e08527a5.webm?t=1746573644\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230660/extras/8c05f830186b1c8af8d39993e08527a5.mp4?t=1746573644\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>With Trivia Tricks Friend Pass you can play online multiplayer with up to 8 players!<br>You can play against each other, or as a team against Trivia Bosses. Choose from 13 base categories and an endless amount of user created Workshop Categories! You can also give a Twitch Chat a podium where they answer when a majority is reached by typing in chat!<br><br>With Friend Pass you will be able to join online lobbies using a Room Code provided by an owner of the full game. As a Friend Pass player you won't be able to make lobbies of your own, and will lack access to certain features such as Character Customization which are only available in the full game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2230660/extras/c65408af8a2fd49a5f8088a106dcb1a4.avif?t=1746573644\" width=600 height=710 /></span>",
